Tested on Ubuntu 16.04

build-essential python git-core autoconf scons

Debian/Ubuntu build:
  debhelper libfltk1.3-dev libhamlib-dev libxft-dev
  libpng-dev zlib1g-dev libexpat-dev portaudio19-dev
  libsamplerate-dev libxmlrpc-core-c3-dev libsndfile-dev
  cdbs quilt libssl-dev libpulse-dev devscripts
  libcurl4-openssl-dev OR  libcurl4-gnutls-dev
  libjpeg62-turbo-dev OR libjpeg8-dev

NB: the OpenSSL licence conflicts with the GPL. Consider using GNU TLS.

(broken)Windows build on Debian/Ubuntu:
  mingw-w64 nsis unzip
